#: ../../source/docs/user_manual/working_with_vector/editing_geometry_attributes.rst:619
# 280c9481b36647b9bf0ee400f416a2aa
msgid "The offset curve tool is a new editing tool. It creates parallel shifts of lines and polygon rings . The tool can be applied to the edited layer (the geometries are modified) or also to background layers (creates copies of the lines / rings and adds it to the the edited layer). It is thus ideally suited for the creation of distance line layers.The displacement is shown at the bottom left of the taskbar."
